CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 16, 1960, pg. 22, reads: "'Nice Going!' - Constable Tommy Smith of the Fifth Ward, sponsor of the Tommy Smith All-Stars softball crew, congratulates his star shortstop, Henry Holt, for his sterling play in short field and offers the same to Mrs. Holt, the star's recent bride. In victory and defeat, Holt has played brilliant ball, observers say.. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Tommy Smith All-Stars softball team shortstop Henry Holt shaking hands with Thomas J. "Tommy" Smith, and Mrs. Holt standing between them, posed in front low bleachers and chain link fence
